s <br />\n而唔係target pathogen本身<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連我一個ug小薯都幻想過<br />\n係practical上有咩難？<br />\n<br />\n定係就係因為safety concern一樣要經歷一堆clinical trial先用得<br />\n而對多數病黎講過晒clinical trial多數自己都好返<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而今次武肺因為係global pandemic 所以反而develop得切？"},{"pid":"c2a1cbb3c98059f5a20f31bdadc6502825424c78","tid":2141521,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"ce69921befb090bf6b76a07c2c48a70ba79f18e4","tid":2141521,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"689080a5de99adc98a87c02d843ae1b49c58c831","tid":2141521,"uid":88663,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T18:04:18.000Z","msg":"有啲人話要房感染武肺，唔可以單靠口罩同洗手，要增強自己免疫力<br />\n<br />\n但係港台有個廣告個醫生話我哋人體係冇武肺嘅抗體，最好嘅預防方法係戴口罩，洗手同埋避免去人多嘅地方（定接觸其他人）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n邊個講法先係真？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T18:05:25.000Z","msg":"兩個講法都無錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T18:09:38.000Z","msg":"第二個講法唔係否定左第一個講法咩？<br />\n<br />\n我理解係，係冇抗體嘅情況下，你免疫系統有幾勁都係冇用"},{"pid":"1e081d15f4dbbc4a4052224e64cc635ebc800e43","tid":2141521,"uid":180142,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"51649a79109bf8b185af47cfa33e777bc63983f5","tid":2141521,"uid":275243,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T18:02:56.000Z","msg":"lm<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實想知好耐<br />\n係lab度antibody<span class=\"red\">好似</span>唔難整<br />\n咁點解一直都唔覺有antibody therapy<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\neg isolate個pathogen之後整個specific Ab<br />\n然後直接inject咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"